ca.uwo.csd.cs2212.team3.WeatherApp

Class DailyForecast

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uwo.csd.cs2212.team3.WeatherApp.WeatherJSON
      • ca.uwo.csd.cs2212.team3.WeatherApp.HourlyForecast
        • ca.uwo.csd.cs2212.team3.WeatherApp.DailyForecast

  • public class DailyForecast
extends HourlyForecast
    This class holds and distributes information about the daily forecast. It is a child of HourlyForecast and uses its Update() function and it's ChangeDataSet(int) function. Being a grandchild of WeatherJSON this class also uses it's functions GetSkyCondition(),GetSkyCode(),and RoundDouble(double).\
    Author:
    Liam Jowahir-Sindrey
